headline: Earnings live: JPMorgan, BlackRock, Wells Fargo, Johnson & Johnson take spotlight as Q3 earnings kick off
summary: Third quarter earnings season is just beginning, and analysts expect S&P 500 companies grew their profits by 8% during the quarter.

headline: Marsh McLennan and Its Businesses Will Brand as Marsh
summary: NEW YORK, October 14, 2025--Marsh McLennan (NYSE: MMC) today announced that it will change its brand to Marsh effective January 2026, and it has created a new unit, Business and Client Services (BCS), to accelerate innovation and centralize investments in operational excellence, data, AI and analytics.
